  "description": "A nighttime long-exposure photograph captures a vibrant fireworks display over a sprawling cityscape and a long bridge extending into dark waters. The fireworks are bursting in shades of gold and white, creating a dramatic spectacle against the black sky. Below, the city is illuminated with numerous lights, forming a dense urban landscape. A prominent bridge with illuminated towers and cables stretches horizontally across the frame, connecting landmasses. The water is dark and calm, reflecting some of the city's and fireworks' light. There are smaller bursts of fireworks visible in the distance adding to the celebratory atmosphere.",
